* Fri Sep  7 2012 Satoru SATOH <ssato@redhat.com> - 0.3.0.99-1
- Quick hack for disk configurations

* Thu Aug 30 2012 Satoru SATOH <ssato@redhat.com> - 0.3.0-1
- Initial packaging
